{"word":"ἄψορρος","slug":"ἄψορρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄψορρος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic for <el>ἀψόρρος</el>\n<p/><i>going back, backwards</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>ἄψορρον</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <i>backward, back again</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}